Pointless allows you to create a "Barack Obama Is Your New Bicycle" clone with unnecessary ease.

Prerequisites:

Python 2.6
Servable (http://servable.appspot.com/)

Running Pointless:

1) Edit config.yaml to your heart's desire
2) Run "./pointless"
3) Check out your Pointless website at http://localhost:8080/

If you can't run ./pointless, make it runnable with "chmod a+x pointless"